- Fixed Our Process section on About Us page: Increased icon size from w-14 h-14 to w-20 h-20 (sm:w-24 sm:h-24) with icon size increased from h-7 w-7 to h-10 w-10 (sm:h-12 sm:w-12) for better visibility. Improved spacing between cards from gap-6 to gap-8 lg:gap-10, increased spacing around icons (mb-4 to mb-6), and increased step number spacing (mb-4 to mb-6). Fixed text color issues: Changed description text from text-white to text-muted-foreground for better readability before hover, ensuring text is clearly visible and matches NXTech branding. Added dark gradient overlay (from-card/95 via-card/70 to-transparent) for better text contrast. Improved process flow visualization with larger step circles (w-12 h-12 to w-14 h-14) and better spacing (gap-4 to gap-6 lg:gap-8). All text now has proper contrast and is readable without relying on hover states.
- Completely redesigned Our Process section to match vertical timeline infographic style: Changed from grid layout to vertical timeline with alternating left/right positioning. Each step now features: large rounded rectangular containers with teal gradient backgrounds (from-[#00c2c7] to darker shades), white circular icon containers with shadows, white text for titles and descriptions ensuring perfect readability, step numbers displayed as "STEP 01", "STEP 02", etc. in primary color, vertical dotted line connecting all steps, connection point circles on the timeline. Steps alternate positioning (even steps on right, odd steps on left) for visual interest. Removed image backgrounds and replaced with solid gradient backgrounds for better text contrast. All text is now white on colored backgrounds, ensuring maximum readability. Icons are prominently displayed in white circles with proper sizing (w-20 h-20 sm:w-24 sm:h-24). Improved spacing and visual hierarchy throughout.
- Updated Get Quote Form to show success popup/modal instead of replacing entire section: Changed form behavior so that when submitted, the form is hidden (opacity-30, pointer-events-none) and a modal popup appears with the success message. The modal features: fixed overlay with backdrop blur, centered modal with gradient background (teal colors), all content centered for better visual appeal, success icon with glow effect (white circle with backdrop blur and shadow), "Thank You!" heading, centered confirmation message, close button in top-right, and centered "Submit Another Request" button. Added smooth animations (fade-in, zoom-in) for better UX. Improved icon styling with outer glow effect and better visual hierarchy. The form remains visible but dimmed in the background, and users can close the modal to reset and submit another request.
- Redesigned Services Industries section with improved UI styling and text visibility: Changed from image-overlay design to card-based layout with image section on top and content section below for better readability. Added dark gradient overlay (from-black/80 via-black/40 to-black/20) on images to ensure white text is always clearly visible. Improved hover effects with card lift animation (hover:-translate-y-2), enhanced shadows (hover:shadow-2xl), and accent line animation. Better text contrast with larger, bolder headings, improved spacing, and icon badges with colored backgrounds. Enhanced visual hierarchy with section separators, better padding, and organized content layout. Added smooth transitions and hover states for all interactive elements. Cards now have white background for content section ensuring perfect text readability at all times.
- Redesigned Additional Services section with attractive UI styling: Enhanced header section with badge, improved typography with gradient text, and better spacing. Improved auto-scrolling cards with larger size (300-320px width), better image section with dark overlay for text contrast, white content section for readability, hover lift animation (hover:-translate-y-2), enhanced shadows (hover:shadow-2xl), accent line animation, and "Learn More" call-to-action with arrow icon. Redesigned grid cards with card-based layout (image on top, content below), dark gradient overlay on images for white text visibility, service name badge overlay on images, hover effects with card lift and enhanced shadows, smooth transitions, and "Explore Service" call-to-action. Added background decorations with blur effects for visual depth. All cards now have consistent styling with better text visibility, attractive hover effects, and improved visual hierarchy.

